members.name: isCarryingChest
members.comment: Gets whether the horse has a chest equipped.

return: true if the horse has chest storage

members.name: setCarryingChest
members.comment: Sets whether the horse has a chest equipped. Removing a chest will also clear the chest's inventory.

param: chest - true if the horse should have a chest

name: org.bukkit.entity.ChestedHorse
comment: Represents Horse-like creatures which can carry an inventory.
